detail.name: Guru
detail.effect:
[End of Your Turn] Place 1 card from your life into your Drop.
[Activate Main] Switch this card in a Battle Area to Rest Mode : During this turn, the next time you use an Extra with a cost of 5 and 《Namekian》 in its special traits from your hand, you don't have to pay the cost.

detail.traits: ナメック星人/ナメック星

faq.question: You play this card when your Leader is FB05-049 <Son Goku>'s back side, you have 5 energy, and your life is at 3. When you activate this card and FB05-049 <Son Goku>'s [End of Your Turn] skills, can you activate this card's skill first, then activate FB05-049 <Son Goku>'s skill when your life is at 2?
リーダーが裏面の「FB05-049　孫悟空」、自分のエナジーが5枚、ライフが3の状態でこのカードが登場しています。このカードと「FB05-049　孫悟空」の【自分のターン終了時】スキルが発動する時、先にこのカードのスキルを発動してライフが2になってから「FB05-049　孫悟空」のスキルを発動することはできますか？
